data.title: Why are Koreans so good at archery and shooting in Olympics?
data.meta_description:
Answer: Because those are mentality games. (Golf is similar.)

But we are also good at fencing (sword point), boxing (fist), and taekwondo (foot), which are sports that require us to move quickly and creatively while avoiding the fastest targets.
